description:
That sounds strange doesn't it.  Do you think I really mean DWI convictions?  Aren't they terrible and bad things.  Well what you are thinking is true, they are bad but now that I have your attention, let me tell you that what we mean by DWI Convictions that are very positive, and that they are vital if you want to be successful as a entrepreneur, a freelancer, solo professional and business owner today.  In fact in today's marketplace where there is always somebody who can do what you do, and sell what you sell, You must be different, unique, and have a reputation for being of value and worthy of being a premium provider.

In this brief course for busy leaders and entrepreneurs i will teach you the true meaning of DWI Convictions, why you must have them and how to acquire them.  You will not be successful if you do not know how to do this!

Stan Hustad
title: You Need "DWI Convictions" To Be a Successful Entrepreneur
